### Class meetings and schedule 

**Time** : Mon Wed 9:30 - 11am

**Location**: 

* *Before January 24*: as part of UBC's response to the COVID-19 omicron variant, lectures will be held online for the first two weeks (synchronously via Zoom; meeting links posted in Canvas)
* *On January 24 and after*: it is expected that class will be held in person in [ESB 2012](https://ssc.adm.ubc.ca/classroomservices/function/viewlocation?userEvent=ShowLocation&buildingID=ESB&roomID=2012) after the first two weeks. In case of any changes to this plan, stay tuned to [UBC Broadcast communications](https://covid19.ubc.ca/) 

**Supplemental Files**: Source files for lectures created using Rmarkdown can be found [here](https://github.com/STAT540-UBC/STAT540-UBC.github.io/tree/master/lectures/lectures_2021/source) 

```{r results = 'asis', echo = FALSE}
knitr::kable(dat_cm[["STAT540"]] %>% select(date, notes, instructor, mode) %>%
  dplyr::rename(Date=date, Topic=notes, Instructor=instructor, Mode=mode),
  "html") %>% 
  kableExtra::kable_styling(full_width = TRUE)
```
